ke `user..name@example.com` with MailAddress, and uses Uri for 10K+ character URLs.\nWhat breaks?","attachments":[],"interactionId":"3b416fad-cb88-492a-8cb6-bf421d9cb301"},"id":"86a2b803-b923-43c4-a16d-8205f56a0e42","timestamp":"2026-05-14T01:12:48.992Z","parentId":"3f7c084a-a72b-4145-a6a4-3081db53e2b9"}
